## ✅ Part 6: Stop and dispose the capture resources

```csharp
public async Task StopCaptureAsync()
{
    if (_session != null)
    {
        await _session.StopCaptureAsync();
        _session.Dispose();
    }

    if (_sink != null)
    {
        _sink.Dispose();
    }
}
```

