You can modify the `Encrypt` method to save the encrypted data to a file instead of just logging it.

```csharp
private void SaveEncryptedData(string encryptedData, string filePath)
{
    File.WriteAllText(filePath, encryptedData);
}

private string LoadEncryptedData(string filePath)
{
